    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184480/extras/c6dbbbb09dd5835e840094d306bb6260.avif?t=1666236109\" width=630 height=138 /></span><br>Off Shore is a first person survival horror game with a nautical theme. You must survive while solving puzzles in hopes of being rescued from a derelict lighthouse.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184480/extras/b70db832bed4f6d529dfc12c5935a6e0.poster.avif?t=1666236109\" width=630 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184480/extras/b70db832bed4f6d529dfc12c5935a6e0.webm?t=1666236109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184480/extras/b70db832bed4f6d529dfc12c5935a6e0.mp4?t=1666236109\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>First Person Gameplay</strong> - Immerse yourself in a dark and cold world of a derelict lighthouse in a first person perspective<br></li><li><strong>Puzzles </strong>- Solve interesting puzzles in an effort to be rescued<br></li><li><strong>Dynamic Threat</strong> - You'll have to be on your toes as a threat lurks in the lighthouse and it could get you at any moment</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184480/extras/c32bca2d2a5bb8dcd9491425ab61a440.poster.avif?t=1666236109\" width=630 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184480/extras/c32bca2d2a5bb8dcd9491425ab61a440.webm?t=1666236109\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_as